name: Where Art Thou Satoshi Nakamoto?
description: "Where Art Thou Satoshi Nakamoto?" is 1 of 7 letters that will be minted as NFTs in order to be shared by true crypto enthusiast and communicate our love and appreciation to Satoshi Nakamoto. Share these letters for all the world to see and Satoshi will surely hear our thanks. The other letters will be released during significant times for Bitcoin and cryptocurrencies. We love you Satoshi.
